<div class="nass margin-top-10"> <p><span id="p1" class="anchor"></span><span class="c3">{وَإِن كُنْتُم جنبا فاطهروا}</span>.<a href="#p1" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p2"></span><span class="c5">يَحْيَى:</span> عَنْ سَعِيدٍ، عَنْ قَتَادَةَ <span class="c2">(عَنِ الْحَسَنِ)</span>،<span class="c5"> عَنْ أَبِي هُرَيْرَةَ قَالَ:</span><a href="#p2" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p3"></span>تَحْتَ كُلِّ شَعْرَةٍ جَنَابَةٌ؛ فَاغْسِلُوا الشَّعْرَ، وَأَنْقُوا الْبَشَرَ ".<a href="#p3" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p> </div>